      "description": "Bikee delivers a premium, fully customizable dashboard for your electric bike, providing real-time access to critical data and powerful control features. Connect instantly to your bike via Bluetooth and unlock a world of smart features designed to enhance your riding experience.\nKey Features:\nAdvanced Dashboard Display\n• Real-time speedometer with sleek digital design\n• Battery level monitoring with voltage information and range estimator\n• Total trip distance tracking in both metric and imperial units\n• Stylish interface that adapts to day/night riding conditions\nCustomizable Power Modes\n• Create and save custom power profiles tailored to your riding preferences\n• Adjust speed limits and throttle settings with precision\n• Easily switch between different regions' riding regulations\n• Specialized modes for various terrains and riding styles\nSmart Navigation\n• Built-in GPS map with route guidance\n• Address search and destination planning\n• Turn-by-turn directions while riding\n• Option to show/hide map based on your preference\nRide Recording & Statistics\n• Track and save all your rides automatically\n• Comprehensive ride history with detailed metrics\n• Achievement system to motivate and track progress\n• Analyze performance data to improve your riding\nIntuitive Controls\n• Adjust pedal assist levels on-the-fly (5 levels from ECO to BOOST)\n• Toggle headlight with a simple tap\n• Quick access to all bike systems through an elegant menu\n• Landscape and portrait modes optimized for all devices\nAdditional Features\n• Multilingual support with 8+ languages\n• Siri shortcuts for hands-free voice control\n• Metric/Imperial unit switching\n• Special power-saving mode for extended range\n• Support community and easy bug reporting\nBikee works seamlessly with modern electric bikes featuring Bluetooth connectivity. Download today and elevate your electric biking experience with the most comprehensive control and navigation app available.",
